>> drop table if exists dm_test

## Prepare table
>> create table dm_test (
        a Int8,
        b Int32
   ) engine = DeltaMerge((a))

>> insert into table dm_test values(1, 2)
>> select * from dm_test
┌─a─┬─b─┐
│ 1 │ 2 │
└───┴───┘

# drop pk is forbidden
>> alter table dm_test drop column a
Received exception from server (version 1.1.54381):
Code: 36. DB::Exception: Received from 127.0.0.1:9000. DB::Exception: Storage engine DeltaMerge doesn't support drop primary key / hidden column: a.
